{"tid":2053012,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［大波Man英領門前撕毀BNO］我宣佈鬥紅行動正式啟動！","createTime":"2020-06-06T03:00:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-06T06:09:40.000Z","uid":247032,"like":55,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":65,"replies":[{"pid":"00106fd10cbd024a06f0c5aa2bd4a0d20c5bf0a5","tid":2053012,"uid":247032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-06T03:00:00.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">首先鬥立法會既親中派議員先 再鬥遍三司十三局<br />\n邊個唔做中國人邊個就係鬼！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/otukJGz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FotukJGz.jpg&h=345d0a72&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【「大波 Man」、高松傑赴英國領事館 撕毀 BNO】<br />\n<br />\n英國首相約翰遜 3 日表示，如果通過國安法，將讓持 BNO 護照港人留英 12 個月，並獲得進一步工作權利，為日後成為英國公民鋪路。今早（6 日），建制派石房有（大波 Man）、高松傑、公民力量林宇星等人到英國駐港總領事館示威，譴責英國「干涉中國內政」，又指香港人不需要 BNO，他們並且當場將自己各自的 BNO 撕毀。<br />\n<br />\n多人並且在傳媒面前宣誓指，「我在此嚴正聲明，只會持有中華人民共和國香港特別行政區護照，堅定擁護一國兩制，全力支持港區國安法」、「國安港安，反獨反奸！」<br />\n<br />\n林宇星表示，「BNO 對於香港人嚟講只係旅遊證件」，而且不能夠正確代表香港人的國民身份，「我哋已經回歸祖國，睇唔到原因點解要續 BNO」。林又說，希望英國不要再在 BNO 議題上「出口術」，企圖破壞中港關係，以及傷害中港兩地人民感情。<br />\n<br />\nsource: <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/standnewshk/photos/a.720050934747196/3146155315470067/?type=3&amp;theater\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fstandnewshk%2Fphotos%2Fa.720050934747196%2F3146155315470067%2F%3Ftype%3D3%26theater&d=bCxsXTpKmrqj5N4FYztdxwg0DHywPMniAnH04N%2BeXdM%3D&h=6b274265\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/standnewshk/photos/a.720050934747196/3146155315470067/?type=3&amp;theater</a>"},{"pid":"db249562b26ddba4bb197a737a9dfd0310f86609","tid":2053012,"uid":247032,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-06T03:01:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kzKXLWS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkzKXLWS.png&h=a1fd028b